name: Sound activated Prime "Fresh-T"
description:
Sound activated transformer equalizer "Fresh-T"

Each shirt is sound activated and engages in a series of sequences when sound is in close proximity of the shirt. The louder the noise the more intense the sequence

"Fresh-T's" are machine washable just detach the battery pack, panel, cables and wash in cold water. Once dry reattach the panel, cables and battery pack.  Then switch the battery pack "on" (insert into custom battery pocket) and your ready to go!
